Titolo: Mudrunner

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Mudrunner, stylised as  MudRunner (Formerly Spintires: Mudrunner) is an off-roading simulation game developed by Saber Interactive and published by Focus Home Interactive. It was released on October 31, 2017 for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One and is a spin-off/sequel of the 2014 Windows-exclusive Spintires, which was developed by Oovee Game Studios. It was later added to the Xbox Game Pass in December 2018. Similar to Spintires, MudRunner has the player control off-road vehicles as they traverse between locations to complete objectives. The game was released in Japan on Nintendo Switch on June 18, 2020. A sequel to MudRunner was released on April 28, 2020 titled SnowRunner.

